{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just the opposite-- we said we're not Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not say 'not Jews.' We said we came from another town which was actually bombarded, and there's fighting going on there, and that-- you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some other not local people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were out-of-town people in that village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And seemingly, they were from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said-- they were starting to murmur to each other, 'Those are Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those are Jews.' OK, we were not too comfortable about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we felt there's no way now to go to any discussion or anything to run to hiding.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then after a couple days, a day staying in that village, we went back to our hometown that we were born and raised, into the hometown, Zarki.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- probably, we were hitchhiking with the Russians, and they took us into town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must have been a few hours just to get into the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We really found in the town really disappointment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody was greeting us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war was not over for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The house that we had was a nice home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- somebody lived in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You cannot just simply--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the people, but I know that they lived there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- But they did not move out in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, my mother pleaded with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, 'Look, I do not need four rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What I really need is just that one room to be able to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the kitchen, we can use, just to-- to share it.'",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he really could not refuse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said, 'How could I refuse you,' he said, 'Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Zborowski?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
